Reactive - ngModel,required


FormGroup - Top Level API
---------
Keeps track of the Values and Validation Status


FormControl 
----------

- Individual form FormControl - 
 track of the Values and Validation Status


interface User {
    name:string;
    account:{
        email:string;
        confirm:string
    }
}
Javascript = API-
---------------
FormGroup -> 'User'
    FormControl -> 'name'
    FormGroup - > 'account'
        FormControl-'email'
        FormControl-'confirm'

DOM Bindings
-----------

formGroupName -> 'User'
    formControlName -> 'name'
    formGroupName - > 'account'
        formControlName-'email'
        formControlName-'confirm'